{"id":"1qc2wu4","title":"This is why having a trading group matters","author":"KindlyCommittee8422","created_utc":1768337369,"score":0,"selftext":"To be honest, I owe a large part of my success to a friend who invited me to a stock trading and sharing group\n\nI'm not someone who watches the market every day, but through these exchanges, I can make better judgments in advance, rather than chasing highs or making emotional decisions\n\nMost importantly: all of this is completely free\n\nThe road ahead is long, but if you're heading in the right direction, compound interest will naturally occur\n\nIf you're also striving to reach your first million, I hope you'll meet the right people and the right circle of friends\n\nWishing everyone successful trading, let's move forward together!","url":"https://www.reddit.com/gallery/1qc2wu4","comments":[{"id":"nzfjdia","author":"Delici81","body":"Can I join too? Just sent you a message:)","score":1,"created_utc":1768341914,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"nzfn483","author":"KindlyCommittee8422","body":"Sure","score":1,"created_utc":1768342992,"is_op":true,"replies":[{"id":"nzheqe4","author":"chubby464","body":"Can I join","score":1,"created_utc":1768364334,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"nzjmfoj","author":"KindlyCommittee8422","body":"Sure","score":1,"created_utc":1768401327,"is_op":true,"replies":[]}]}]},{"id":"nzuacaj","author":"ericphiser","body":"Could i join as well?","score":1,"created_utc":1768527597,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"nzxc42b","author":"Delici81","body":"Sure","score":1,"created_utc":1768573858,"is_op":false,"replies":[]}]}]},{"id":"nzfy4qy","author":"lulutina2001","body":"me too can i join?","score":1,"created_utc":1768346369,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"nzfzg65","author":"KindlyCommittee8422","body":"Sure, hope this helps","score":1,"created_utc":1768346792,"is_op":true,"replies":[]}]},{"id":"nzg1ckn","author":"DunkTheMuss","body":"Please can I join! 🚀","score":1,"created_utc":1768347408,"is_op":false,"r